videos.headline: Moore gives Nevada early lead with TD
videos.description: Nevada RB Kelton Moore rushes up the middle for a 4-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Reverse pass puts Boise State in scoring territory
videos.description: Boise State WR Cedrick Wilson takes the reverse and passes to QB Brett Rypien down the sidelines for a 15-yard gain.

videos.headline: Broncos force first turnover on INT
videos.description: Nevada QB Ty Gangi forces a pass into heavy coverage and is picked off by Boise State S Kekoa Nawahine in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Boise State capitalizes on turnover with rushing TD
videos.description: Alexander Mattison cuts to the outside for a 13-yard touchdown following the interception from Nevada.

videos.headline: Nevada's Moore breaks out for big gain
videos.description: Kelton Moore bounces to the outside for a 34-yard gain to put the Wolf Pack in the red zone.

videos.headline: Nevada's Gangi connects with Armstrong for TD
videos.description: Ty Gangi lobs a pass to the back corner of the end zone to Trevion Armstrong for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Broncos QB Rypien finds Wilson for long TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien lets a pass fly over the middle to Cedrick Wilson for a 44-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Nevada's Gangi commits 2nd INT
videos.description: Ty Gangi tries to force a pass on third down and is picked off by Curtis Weaver.

videos.headline: Broncos Wolpin rushes up the middle for TD
videos.description: Ryan Wolpin goes up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Broncos Rypien slings 2nd TD
videos.description: Brett Rypien fires a pass over the middle to Jake Roh for a 25-yard touchdown late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Broncos WR Wilson fires 2nd long pass of game
videos.description: WR Cedrick Wilson throws a pass over the middle to backup QB Montell Cozart for a 31-yard gain.

videos.headline: Boise States' Mattison fakes out defense for rushing TD
videos.description: Alexander Mattison jukes out the defenders for a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Nevada's Demps hauls in long pass
videos.description: Ty Gangi connects with Wyatt Demps for a 30-yard gain.

videos.headline: Wolf Pack continues to struggle with 3rd turnover
videos.description: Ty Gangi tries forcing a pass down the sidelines and is intercepted by Tyler Horton in the fourth quarter.
